{"tid":1296772,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"日日訓醒都好累，好似無訓過一樣。","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T20:35:49.000Z","uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"475280434f265c7f1f8a93c45f1dd8750f3d2ecc","tid":1296772,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"試過訓前落街跑步，聽音樂，睇書，又試過係6-9小時裡面搵一個啱自己訓的時間，耐唔耐會有一天訓得好好，一醒嗰刻好似差足電咁，但大部份日子一起身之後成個人會覺得好累，無咩精力咁。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打有妙計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b808402f984c0af869df50663639b705e947670","tid":1296772,"uid":69820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"475280434f265c7f1f8a93c45f1dd8750f3d2ecc","tid":1296772,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"試過訓前落街跑步，聽音樂，睇書，又試過係6-9小時裡面搵一個啱自己訓的時間，耐唔耐會有一天訓得好好，一醒嗰刻好似差足電咁，但大部份日子一起身之後成個人會覺得好累，無咩精力咁。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打有妙計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"出黎遊行 包你精神<br />\n7.13 光復上水"},{"pid":"1fac20460a2957dc7bdf3effe9c98a01f62335d4","tid":1296772,"uid":33609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"其實我都呢個狀態好幾年  加上自己一D 情緒問題 <br />\n無左細個訓醒好精神爽利 充滿希望嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n加上香港依家咁... 訓得再差D  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 連薯仔你D 文都無心機睇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢就習慣左   訓得唔好  果日都要過  <br />\n<br />\n唯一係有一期轉左工  份工好緊張  要一早起身  又要有體力勞動 <br />\n養成左早睡早起   基本上果一年晚晚都可以訓得好好  <br />\n<br />\n之後依家再轉左份工  <br />\n坐office 返工無乜郁動   <br />\n收工無輪夜晚點做運動  逼自己晚晚跑步,  訓前睇書 打坐<br />\n都去唔返之前咁好訓"},{"pid":"4a4d4aa7c345c42d3d4622ec6df15b5d8c670ef2","tid":1296772,"uid":205231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"應該係亞健康出現問題"},{"pid":"b9b1535e92bbde7ac46dfa90126491e966cc6bb6","tid":1296772,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:12:04.000Z","msg":"中醫病友fb gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/954306168239427/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F954306168239427%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2b12a6eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/954306168239427/</a><br />\n中醫病友tg gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=18a0b0b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA</a><br />\n<br />\n男，20-25歲,病左5年,輕度肥胖<br />\n睇過13個醫師，計埋好快放棄嘅至少20<br />\n<br />\n症狀：疲倦,不精神,四肢無力,手：愈近末梢，愈少力。切兩個橙好攰，要休息。合上眼後指頭不太能分辨尖/頓。乏力以手為主，職業治療檢查出我手小肌肉做重複性動作好快攰。腳：行約1小時覺攰，要休息。全身：試過拎3.5kg行10分鐘，超攰。有時覺肚向下the。有時膝痛。有手腳心汗。腳板脫皮，病發後腳掌較以前闊，要買加加闊版鞋。<br />\n無覺得凍/熱。大小便正常。無失眠。無骨傷史。無地貧。<br />\n<br />\n病因：我估5-8年前，食太多龜苓膏涼茶搞到成日腹瀉，之後個人慢慢愈來愈攰<br />\n<br />\n近一年處方：<a href=\"https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotos.app.goo.gl%2F9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=e0d5bc53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6</a><br />\n<br />\n近日處方有十全大補、黃精、杞子，每次飲完都微微有力，疑整體藥量太少/熟地太少（見張鍚純開過４兩）/沖劑無力<br />\n<br />\n睇過既醫師:<br />\n黃志忠 客座副教授 中大中醫專科診所暨臨床教硏中心<br />\n莫飛智 師從鄧鐵濤 前港大助理教授 中大客座副教授<br />\n馬劍穎（睇過幾次放棄） 一級講師 浸大中醫藥診所<br />\n李廣冀 遠志中醫<br />\n商海峰 林鐵志 專科門診 博愛醫院-香港中文大學中醫教研中心(元朗)<br />\n葉嘉禮 陸葉中醫診所<br />\n仲有街邊藥房中醫唔打出黎<br />\n<br />\n西醫:睇過腦神經內科,等緊內科神經傳導檢查。照過胸背x光。有脂肪肝。 肝酵素高。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法：<br />\nFb messager <a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=f7186a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\nTg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=10bcf9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a>"},{"pid":"68af3ceb6c34b724b9571bd6fbfc988e51ae1675","tid":1296772,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"試過中醫未，有中醫學生介紹黃斌 張清苓"},{"pid":"880eb1935ce0949cfe457108d22825cc063c4c0c","tid":1296772,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fac20460a2957dc7bdf3effe9c98a01f62335d4","tid":1296772,"uid":33609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"其實我都呢個狀態好幾年  加上自己一D 情緒問題 <br />\n無左細個訓醒好精神爽利 充滿希望嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n加上香港依家咁... 訓得再差D  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 連薯仔你D 文都無心機睇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢就習慣左   訓得唔好  果日都要過  <br />\n<br />\n唯一係有一期轉左工  份工好緊張  要一早起身  又要有體力勞動 <br />\n養成左早睡早起   基本上果一年晚晚都可以訓得好好  <br />\n<br />\n之後依家再轉左份工  <br />\n坐office 返工無乜郁動   <br />\n收工無輪夜晚點做運動  逼自己晚晚跑步,  訓前睇書 打坐<br />\n都去唔返之前咁好訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最近嘗試在臨訓前跑30分鐘步，然後沖涼，食條蒸粟米同飲杯熱茶，然後聽陣音樂再訓，效果好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd649cb9f215b7670ffe88b95115682adf8484f0","tid":1296772,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4d4aa7c345c42d3d4622ec6df15b5d8c670ef2","tid":1296772,"uid":205231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"應該係亞健康出現問題"}